{"tid":1906113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣網友整左個「武漢肺炎歷史軌跡比對」，自動檢查你是否碰過武漢肺炎患者","createTime":"2020-03-01T17:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T12:35:42.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18fbc273ee40fad13db350a7176854439123956c","tid":1906113,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"根據PTT的網友分享「武漢肺炎歷史軌跡比對」這個網站，這是g0v推出一個可以自動檢查你是否碰過武漢肺炎患者的網站，主要的原理就是透過你在Google地圖記錄你的時間軸足跡，比對目前指揮中心公布的患者的足跡，看看兩邊的足跡是否有重疊。當然，你也可以手動自己檢查，但是隨著病例越來越多，當然還是線上直接比對來得方便。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎歷史軌跡比對設計的相當直覺，應該你一連上去就可以看懂該怎麼做。網站上有四個步驟照著走就好了。如果你擔心隱私的問題，網站上一開始也先表示，這個程式藉由比對你的手機歷史位置記錄，來判斷是否曾與病患接觸。基於隱私考量，你的資料只會在本地端處理，不會上傳到任何網路主機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/547301/original/00862ed9ea04cfb19560426b8728ba9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F547301%2Foriginal%2F00862ed9ea04cfb19560426b8728ba9e.jpg&h=eb21025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然前提是你先前必須先讓你的手機定位記錄功能有開啟，允許Google地圖記錄。如果沒有的話，那麼這個網站就不適合你查詢。不過，你現在開始開啟記錄的功能，日後說不定還是用得到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/547302/original/5fae8b86b462c8f7296e8c5c2af6ea01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F547302%2Foriginal%2F5fae8b86b462c8f7296e8c5c2af6ea01.jpg&h=5943a154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再來就是到第三步，把你剛剛下載的資料載入進行針對足跡的發生時間以及地點來比對，看看是否有相吻合。根據他們網站的說明，為了保護隱私，他們用的比對方法是採用了名為 ST hash (SpaceTime hash)的演算法得到雜湊值，然後再針對你的時間軌跡資料透過相同的演算法求出雜湊值，藉此求出你是否有在特定的時間點與患者足跡重疊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/547304/original/2cd1cbf06af1a1c3ad303a59604b6be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F547304%2Foriginal%2F2cd1cbf06af1a1c3ad303a59604b6be2.jpg&h=ded9da99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後就顯示出比對結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/547305/original/b318723ee649491f8f9a4de5970d27ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F547305%2Foriginal%2Fb318723ee649491f8f9a4de5970d27ff.jpg&h=e47d6b2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"816d70f4eac2caed168c06da30be7ec943d4c688","tid":1906113,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"1. 請莫乃光議員要求食物及衞生局提供病患歷史軌跡<br />\n2. 創科局到底做咩撚野"},{"pid":"5704895658a0e7dd5e86f67b6905bab0b66fcb14","tid":1906113,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"Source code on github: <a href=\"https://github.com/yjlou/2019-nCov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fyjlou%2F2019-nCov&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=443b78fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/yjlou/2019-nCov</a>"},{"pid":"d1a90eeb078b3256e494f85f2edc2fbe032dc26a","tid":1906113,"uid":52311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"但台灣唔公佈自己台灣人足跡wo<br />\n話會比人奇視"},{"pid":"82fcc0240546653cbf60528ba359f180d244f74b","tid":1906113,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"香港地方咁細<br />\n總有一個係附近<br />\n<br />\n例如北角社區爆發<br />\n下面黨鐵轉車站一日幾萬人經過<br />\n點追蹤到?"},{"pid":"2f1739c315e4e09e48a8300a053d9ee663101f50","tid":1906113,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"推，好似唔錯，雖然未必適合香港<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"960be047315eb471e1ffd82ab6d456b4dc3dd94e","tid":1906113,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82fcc0240546653cbf60528ba359f18